Posted By: Keith O'Leary
I offer a 3 day no questions asked return policy and will hold any card(s) for 60 days. When I get the green, you'll get the cardboard and plastic. if you'd like bigger or more detailed scans of anything, feel free to ask.



[URL="http://i45.photobucket.com/albums/f92/vwtdi55/Turkey%20Reds/t3_moran_b205.jpg"][/URL]









N142 Duke Cyclists. There are only 7 cards in the N142 set, 4 baseball players and 3 cyclists. Oversized (6 1/4 X 9") cabinet cards rarely offered. Sanger has a small tear on right side edge, Zimmerman has a crescent shaped crease at the bottom with a smaller one to its right as seen. sold.

Extra Large W Duke & Sons Co Premium card. In the World Tobacco Index Volume 3. "Duke Misc issue. Group 6-2-1A Studies of Girls 165 X 105 cm. Back has "What we claim", front has Cross Cut Cigarettes, 5-8 seen". 9 3/4 X 17" with original mailing envelope. Excellent condition with all of its gold gilt edge. The only one I've ever seen. 1500.
